Buckley

A simple blogging tool built for Google App Engine with the goal of high performance and flexibility

Install

Grab the App Engine SDK:

  http://code.google.com/appengine/downloads.html

Then run the demo via:

  dev_appserver.py .

Customize your "routes" via app.yaml

